                <h1>Arizona Background Check Laws: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>Arizona background check laws vary depending on the context, primarily in employment and gun purchase scenarios. Employers must comply with federal and state regulations when conducting checks, ensuring candidate privacy. For firearm purchases, background checks are mandatory to affirm buyer eligibility, promoting public safety.</p>
